==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sandworm
<hw>Sand"worm`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>Any one of numerous species of annelids which burrow
in the sand of the seashore.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>Any species of
annelids of the genus <gen>Sabellaria</gen>. They construct firm tubes
of agglutinated sand on rocks and shells, and are sometimes destructive
to oysters.</def> <sd>(c)</sd> <def>The chigoe, a species of
flea.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sandwort</ent>⟦br⟧
